SYSTEMD_LOGIND_NEW_SESSION New session %{INT:[systemd][session][id]:int} of user %{USERNAME:[user][name]}\.
SYSTEMD_LOGIND_SESSION_LOGGED_OUT Session %{INT:[systemd][session][id]:int} logged out\. Waiting for processes to exit\.
SYSTEMD_LOGIND_SESSION_REMOVED Removed session %{INT:[systemd][session][id]:int}\.

APP_SYSTEMD_LOGIND (%{SYSTEMD_LOGIND_NEW_SESSION}|%{SYSTEMD_LOGIND_SESSION_LOGGED_OUT}|%{SYSTEMD_LOGIND_SESSION_REMOVED})

